TERMINATION AND ENFORCEMENT

1. AUTOMATIC TERMINATION
   Any violation of Conditions 1, 2, 3, or 4 immediately and automatically
   terminates all rights granted under this License. Upon termination you
   must cease all use, distribution, and hosting of the software and any
   derivative works.

2. CURE PERIOD
   If you become aware that you are in violation, you have 14 (fourteen)
   calendar days from the date you first knew (or reasonably should have
   known) of the violation to bring yourself into full compliance. If you
   cure the violation within this 14-day window, your rights under this
   License are reinstated. If you do not cure within 14 days, termination
   is permanent and no reinstatement is available.

3. LEGAL ACTION
   Violations of this License constitute copyright infringement under
   applicable law (including but not limited to the Indian Copyright Act,
   1957 and international copyright treaties). The Licensor reserves all
   rights to pursue legal remedies including:
     • Injunctive relief (takedown of infringing deployments or repositories)
     • Damages for copyright infringement
     • Recovery of legal costs and attorney fees
     • Any other relief available under applicable law

4. REPORTING VIOLATIONS
   To report a violation of this License, open an issue at:
     https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu/vridhira-frontend/issues
   or contact the author directly via the GitHub profile above.

